    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"519727\">Alice Ryhl</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/291565-Help/topic/OnceCell/near/472885872\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Actually, <code>include/linux/once.h</code> is not completely identical to <code>std::sync::Once</code></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Right, all <code>DO_ONCE()</code>s shared the same spinlock apparently.</p>",
